 of fit $\\chi^2_{tot}/dof \\simeq 0.769$ is\nachieved, if the chemical freeze-out temperature of hadrons is about $T_h=150$\nMeV, while the one for all (anti)nuclei is $T_A=174-175.2$ MeV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 11 Apr 2020 20:33:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Nov 2020 21:21:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-22"}
